description: Numbers with 4 zeros in Fibonacci numbers mod m.
comments: Conjecture: m is on this list iff m is an odd number all of whose factors are on this list or m is twice such an odd number.A001176(a(n)) = A128924(a(n),1) = 4. - _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jan 17 2014
